<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ل وع:</span> <span class="c2">(لَوْعَةُ)</span> الْحُبِّ حُرْقَتُهُ، وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(لَاعَهُ)</span> الْحُبُّ مِنْ بَابِ قَالَ. وَ <span class="c2">(الْتَاعَ)</span> فُؤَادُهُ احْتَرَقَ مِنَ الشَّوْقِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>